  "The most effective proven technology that is economically achievable for controlling pollution from a specific source": "",
  "Experimental technologies still in research and development": "",
  "The most expensive technology regardless of its effectiveness": "",
  "BAT is a regulatory standard requiring polluters to use the most effective technology that is commercially available and economically feasible. It ensures that pollution control keeps pace with technological advances while considering costs.": "",
  "What is a 'consent decree' in environmental law?": "",
