  "Captive breeding can replace pollution control as a conservation strategy": "",
  "Only banning pesticides was necessary for the falcon's recovery": "",
  "The peregrine falcon recovery shows that while removing the pollutant (DDT ban) was essential, active conservation measures (captive breeding, release programs, nest site protection) were also needed. This multi-pronged approach -- eliminating pollution sources AND actively assisting recovery -- is a model for other species.": ""
